  <summary date="2024-08-22T18:36:29Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Ensuring Nationwide Access to a Better Life Experience Act or the ENABLE Act

This bill makes permanent three tax provisions relating to ABLE (Achieving a Better Life Experience)&#160;Accounts established to assist disabled individuals, specifically provisions allowing increased contributions to such accounts, the allowance of a retirement savings contribution tax credit up to $1,000, and allowing a tax-free rollover from a qualified tuition (529 plan) to an ABLE account.&#160;</summary>
